<title type="html"><![CDATA[It Does not Matter How Long You study with someone for you to be a major Scholar]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=1438&amp;p=1539#p1539"><![CDATA[
